{
  "texts": [
    "Otherwise, it's non-trivial.",
    "For example, the comment \"set a to 1\" for a=1 is trivial.",
    "Specifically, we define NR = Non-trivial Comments(optimized output) Correct Comments(optimized output)where Non-trivial Comments represents the number of nontrivial comments and Correct Comments represents the number of correct comments, to evaluate the quality of the comments appended by DeGPT.",
    "Like CR, we also manually calculate NR to ensure its trustworthiness during the evaluation.",
    "The higher NR is, the better the quality of the appended comments is."
  ]
}